      "title": "Person arrested for transporting 1,000l diesel",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); One person has been arrested for illegally transporting diesel in a cab in Hiniduma area.",
        "Police said that an illegal stock of diesel was found while checking the cab at a roadblock.",
        "Accordingly, 1,000 liters of diesel was found inside the cab at the time.",
        "The arrested 31-year-old suspect, identified as a resident of Pelawatte, has been released on police bail after being informed to appear before the Udugama Magistrate's Court.",
        "NTC to take action against over 100 buses for overcharging passengers"
      ],
